=== 生活功能 ===

==== 微信支付 ====
{{main|微信支付|{{tsl|en|WeChat red envelope|微信红包}}}}
{{seealso|财付通}}

*支付功能
微信支付支持银行卡转账、扫码支付、近场通信等时下流行的多种移动支付手段，并在中国大陸、香港和马来西亚实现本地化，绑定了银行卡的用户可以利用微信來支付账单、购买商品和服务、並實現向其他用户转账、甚至可以在支持微信支付的商店消费或进行跨境消费。被称为“小程序”的第三方通过开发轻量级的“应用程序中的应用程序”来提供部分服务<ref>{{Cite web |title=When One App Rules Them All: The Case of WeChat and Mobile in China |url=https://a16z.com/2015/08/06/wechat-china-mobile-first/ |date=August 6, 2015 |last=Chan |first=Connie |website=Andreessen Horowitz |accessdate=2017-10-22 |archive-date=2018-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181110060624/https://a16z.com/2015/08/06/wechat-china-mobile-first/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

微信支付導入微信的[[电子现金|电子现金]]服务，允许用户进行移动支付，在用户之间汇款<ref>{{Cite web |title=WeChat now supports payments between users and one-click payments {{!}} Finance Magnates |url=http://www.financemagnates.com/fintech/payments/wechat-now-supports-payments-between-users-and-one-click-payments/ |accessdate=2015-12-13 |language=en-US |website=Fin Tech {{!}} Finance Magnates |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201249/http://www.financemagnates.com/fintech/payments/wechat-now-supports-payments-between-users-and-one-click-payments/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。每位微信用户都有属于自己的微信支付帐户。用户将帐户绑定银行卡，或从其他用户收款可以获得零钱。绑定信用卡的用户只能向供应商付钱，不能补充零钱。微信支付可用于电子现金以及供应商付款<ref name="fastco-redpacket2">{{Cite web |title=How Social Cash Made WeChat The App For Everything |url=https://www.fastcompany.com/3065255/china-wechat-tencent-red-envelopes-and-social-money |accessdate=4 January 2017 |website=Fast Company |archive-date=2018-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180914072143/https://www.fastcompany.com/3065255/china-wechat-tencent-red-envelopes-and-social-money |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。截至2016年3月，微信支付全球用户超过3亿。2016年4月，微信斥资1亿人民币加快市场拓展<ref>{{Cite web |title=WeChat Pay invests USD 15 M to support its service providers |url=http://allchinatech.com/8666-2/ |accessdate=2016-04-22 |language=en-US |dead-url=yes |website=AllChinaTech |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424152206/http://www.allchinatech.com/8666-2/ |archive-date=2016-04-24 }}</ref>。

*金融功能
微信支付提供信用卡还款、微粒贷借钱等基础金融功能，用户还可以从微信支付页面中直接进入腾讯理财通，在理财通中购买基金等其他金融产品。

*社会服务功能
微信支付中整合了部分社会服务功能，用户可以在微信支付中便捷完成水、电、气等生活缴费，浏览所在城市的气象、医疗、保险、交通、政务及公益等服务信息。

城市服务于2015年上线<ref>{{Cite web |title=Why WeChat City Services Is A Game-Changing Move For Smartphone Adoption |url=https://techcrunch.com/2015/04/24/why-wechat-city-services-is-a-game-changing-move-for-smartphone-adoption/ |date=2015-04-24 |last=Stanciu |first=Tudor |website=TechCrunch |access-date=2017-05-18 |archive-date=2019-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211145109/http://techcrunch.com/2015/04/24/why-wechat-city-services-is-a-game-changing-move-for-smartphone-adoption/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，涵盖北京、上海、广州、深圳等27个城市<ref>{{Cite web |title=微信又一超赞新功能接入 |url=http://toutiao.com/a4814935978/ |accessdate=2015-12-13 |website=今日头条 |archive-date=2016-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408021407/http://toutiao.com/a4814935978/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。城市服务包括门诊预约、水电费和交通罚款缴纳和车票预订等功能<ref>{{Cite web |title=WeChat City Services |url=http://blog.grata.co/wechat-city-services/ |accessdate=2015-12-13 |language=en-US |website=Grata |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222140248/http://blog.grata.co/wechat-city-services/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年，微信推出热度地图展示人流密集度。[[Quartz|Quartz]]专栏作者{{le|乔希·霍维茨|Josh Horwitz}}质疑中国政府利用该功能监控非法集会，但这一消息未得到证实<ref>{{Cite web |title=WeChat's new heat map feature lets users—and Chinese authorities—see where crowds are forming |url=http://qz.com/518908/wechats-new-heat-map-feature-lets-users-and-chinese-authorities-see-where-crowds-are-forming/ |accessdate=2016-10-07 |last1=Horwitz |first1=Josh |website=Quartz |archive-date=2016-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010122647/http://qz.com/518908/wechats-new-heat-map-feature-lets-users-and-chinese-authorities-see-where-crowds-are-forming/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==== 微信卡包 ====
用戶可通過微信公衆號、城市服務等渠道領取會員卡、優惠券、電子證件及QR碼並會保存在微信卡包中。

