2016年11月30日，加拿大[[公民实验室|公民实验室]]发布了针对微信关键字过滤问题的研究报告。研究发现关键词过滤仅针对使用中国大陆手机号码的注册用户；关键词被审查之后用户不会收到提示，而且群组聊天中的审查更为严格；关键词列表并非一成不变，新发现的关键词常与新闻事件有关。另外，微信自带的浏览器会对中国用户屏蔽一系列网站，而中国大陆之外的用户却可以使用微信自带的浏览器访问这些网站。<ref>{{Cite web |title=One App, Two Systems: How WeChat uses one censorship policy in China and another internationally |url=https://citizenlab.ca/2016/11/wechat-china-censorship-one-app-two-systems/ |accessdate=2016-12-03 |author=Lotus Ruan, Jeffrey Knockel, Jason Q. Ng, and Masashi Crete-Nishihata |date=2016-11-30 |publisher=[[公民实验室|公民实验室]] |language=en |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180112034933/https://citizenlab.ca/2016/11/wechat-china-censorship-one-app-two-systems/ |archive-date=2018-01-12 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://citizenlab.ca/2016/12/%E4%B8%80app%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7/ |title=“一APP两制”：微信如何区别审查中国及海外用户 |author=Lotus Ruan, Jeffrey Knockel, Jason Q. Ng, and Masashi Crete-Nishihata |date=2016-12-01 |publisher=[[公民实验室|公民实验室]] |language=zh-hans |dead-url=no |access-date=2018-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180112035042/https://citizenlab.ca/2016/12/%E4%B8%80app%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%B6%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8F%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%96%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7/ |archive-date=2018-01-12 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://citizenlab.ca/2018/08/%E6%9C%AA%E9%98%85%E5%85%88%E7%84%9A%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E5%9C%88%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90/ |title=“未阅先焚” 微信朋友圈图片过滤功能分析 |author=Jeffrey Knockel, Lotus Ruan, Masashi Crete-Nishihata, and Ron Deibert |date=2018-08-15 |publisher=[[公民实验室|公民实验室]] |language=zh-hans |access-date=2018-09-25 |archive-date=2018-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180925142020/https://citizenlab.ca/2018/08/%E6%9C%AA%E9%98%85%E5%85%88%E7%84%9A%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E5%9C%88%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年5月7日，加拿大公民实验室再次发布了针对微信关键字过滤问题的研究报告。这次研究发现，微信对中国注册和非中国注册的账户都进行了内容监视。<ref>{{cite web |title=We Chat, They Watch. How International Users Unwittingly Build up WeChat’s Chinese Censorship Apparatus |url=https://citizenlab.ca/2020/05/we-chat-they-watch/ |access-date=2020-05-08 |author=Jeffrey Knockel, Christopher Parsons, Lotus Ruan, Ruohan Xiong, Jedidiah Crandall, and Ron Deibert |archive-date=2020-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821215014/https://citizenlab.ca/2020/05/we-chat-they-watch/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

